Changelog v1.0.0 DarkRealms

Added

	• Blasting recipes for raw metals blocks :check:

	• Recipes netherite ingot from fiery :check:

	• Inventory items weight items: raw ores, gems 1 => 2-4, ingots 1 => 3-8, chests 1 => 16, shields 1 => 16-24, waystone => 20, logs => 4 :check:

	• Custom items for tools upgrades stone -> iron, iron -> gold, gold -> diamond.  :check:

	• Custom items for weapons upgrades stone -> iron, iron -> gold, gold -> diamond. :check:

	• Craft for Andesite/copper/brass casing from create :check:

	• Biome related mob spawns is not yet implemented !!!

        • Spells books crafting in enchanting infusion

        • Quest system work in progress

Changed 

	• Config for thermal ore generation: remove lead, nickel ores :check:

	• Maximum inventory weight 3000 => 2500 :check:

	• Glowsticks completely removed :check:

	• Rotor, stator from tfmg completely removed :check:

	• Iron and above tools tiers now crafting using smithing table from parts and upgrades :check:

	• Tools upgrades crafts from custom items :WIP:

	• Iron and above weapons tiers now crafting using smithing table from parts and upgrades  :check:

	• Weapons upgrades parts drop from different hostile :Check:

		• Iron upgrades shards drops from zombies, skeletons, husks

		• Gold upgrades shards drops from wither-skeletons, blazes, strays

		• Diamond upgrades shards drops from endermans, pillagers
	
		• Netherite upgrade shards drops from piglins, piglin brute

	• Tools and weapons recipes removed, except wood, stone tiers :check:

        • Tools upgrades duplicate :check:

	• Almost every create and create addons recipes completely removed, and many parts may find in structures or buying from villagers.
For example: mechanical drill has no longer craft recipe, but it is still could be find in Tinkerers workshop structure      :WIP:

        • Spell books crafted from custom item in infusion from apotheosis

